Israeli pianist Itamar Golan, regarded by international music
critics as an equal partner who perfectly matches Chung's musical
conceptions.
</P>
<P>
In a career spanning more than 25 years, Chung is one of the
most outstanding musicians in the world, gaining great fame and
performing with many great orchestras.  
