<HEADLINE> People's Daily Calls for National Unity, Stability (4) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Everything is determined by strength, and hegemonism ventures
to grossly interfere in the internal affairs of other countries
and even launch wars and destroy peace because it has powerful
economies and military forces, the article points out.
</P>
<P>
"Why we can achieve triumph in opposing the hegemonic acts by
the U.S.-led NATO lies in the fact that the Chinese people has
stood up. The Chinese nation has become stronger and more
prosperous," the commentary says, adding that the struggle has
enabled the Chinese people to be more determined to focus on
economic developments.
</P>
<P>
Facing competitions in the economic, technological and national
defense areas worldwide, it is imperative for China to concentrate
on developing advanced science and technology and strengthening
its economy and national defense, it says.
</P>
<P>
Only in this way, can China never be defeated, it adds.
</P>
<P>
International hostile forces continue to put pressure on China,
and engage in "westernizing China" and "separating China", it
points out, adding that it is imperative for China to maintain
unity and stability to deal with this.
</P>
</TEXT>
