passenger car and a van at a crossing in Kanagawa Prefecture,
southeast of Tokyo, leaving one dead and four injured.
</P>
<P>
In Hokkaido, meanwhile, an elderly couple died after the car
they were in dived into the sea in Kushiro on Japan's northernmost
main island, the report said. 
