<TEXT>
<P>
ISLAMABAD, May 7 (Xinhua) -- Pakistan's Anti-Narcotics Force (
ANF) on Saturday raided a huge narcotic dump some 120 kilometers
northeast of Turbat in the mountains of Panjgur, Balochistan
Province, and recovered 5.75 tons of hashish, according to the
Associated Press of Pakistan (APP).
</P>
